files:
-  dhcp-2-dns - script for the mikrotik dhcp service
-  force-dns-usage - NAT rules to force usage of the DNS regardless client config. Also a netwatch to monitor dns availability and manipulate NAT accorfingly
-  oxidized - rules for oxidized to avoid backups due to dhcp2dns changes


NOTE: The base of the 'dhcp-2-dns' script is NOT mine.  It comes from https://forum.mikrotik.com/viewtopic.php?t=119469
